      <title>捷克总理称欧洲需要美国向普京展现实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/europe-needs-us-to-project-strength-to-putin-czech-premier-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克总理表示，欧洲需要美国展现实力，以阻止俄罗斯采取更激进的举动，并警告盟友不要在结束乌克兰战争的任何过程中采取“绥靖”政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/europe-needs-us-to-project-strength-to-putin-czech-premier-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:16:11 GMT</pubDate>
